OL,5, A justice bill giving mandatory life   
OL,6, sentences to the killers of emergency  
OL,7, services workers has become law after  
OL,8, receiving Royal Assent.                
OL,10,FLissie Harper campaigned for "Harper's 
OL,11,FLaw" after her husband was killed in   
OL,12,FSulhamstead, Berkshire, in August 2019.
OL,14,FPC Andrew Harper, a 28-year-old Thames 
OL,15,FValley Police officer from Wallingford,
OL,16,FOxfordshire, was dragged to his death  
OL,17,Fby a getaway car.                      
OL,19,FThree teenagers were jailed for        
OL,20,Fmanslaughter.                          
